Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:06.39,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,1220,4000,4800)\pos(713.864,796.854)}Liu Bei Seeks the Virtuous
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was passing through when a child led me to visit your esteemed presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:01:01.31,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,6000,6200)\pos(189.263,380)}Sīmǎ Huī\NStyled: Décāo)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, you shouldn't keep secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here today in order to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:13.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5500,5700)\pos(1216.156,418.181)}Liú Bèi\N Styled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you, Liu Biao had me attend a meeting in Xiāngyáng —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,— but Cai Mao tried to harm me, so I fled them and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered that from your facial expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard of your great reputation, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has it to this day you have no foundations of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate are ever-changing. That is why I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}The reason why you haven't yet accomplished your great undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:02:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — is because there are no virtuous sage men around to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I may not be able  —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}But with me are ministers{\i1} Sūn Qián, Mí Zhú, {\i0}and \N{\i1}Jiǎn Yōng{\i0}, and generals {\i1}Yúncháng, Yìdé, {\i0}and {\i1}Zǐlóng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}All loyal and supportive, \Nhow could you not count them as sage men?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}Sir, why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Guan Yu, Zhang Fei, Zhao Yun are warriors rivaling of ten-thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}But its pitiable that they aren't made more use of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Sun Qian, Jian Yong, \Nand Mi Zhu are inexpert literati —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318} — Not men of grand strategies and statesmanship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}Teacher, your words are most correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}I have searched for such able men before —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}— but haven't had the chance to meet a man of such talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}Xuande, is it not like how Confucius once said:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\i1}"Within a township of ten families, \Nyou will find one who is venerable and virtuous."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,995.182)}{\bord14.318}Why claim there are no men of talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Forgive my ignorance on this matter. I'd like to ask your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}The great heroes and prodigies of today are already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(726.136,1002.273)}Sir Xuande must go inquire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(726.136,1002.273)}I wish to know who these prodigies are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\i1}'Sleeping Dragon'{\i0} and{\i1} 'Fledgling Phoenix'{\i0}\N With either by your side, peace can be brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Please explain sir, who are these\N {\i1}Sleeping Dragon {\i0}and{\i1}Fledgling Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,General, feel free to stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be time to talk again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:23.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The reason why you haven't yet accomplished your great undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:28.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — is because there are no virtuous sage men around to assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:38.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Dragon and Fledgling Phoenix... \NWith even one by your side, peace can be brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:48.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun unsuccessfully searched for Liu Bei outside Xiāngyáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:53.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When he saw water prints from the east of the Tán-Creek to the west —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:58.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— he figured Liu Bei came back to Xinye, and returned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,However, even after he returned to Xinye, he couldn't find Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun felt very worried  —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — so he searched the entire western bank of the Tán-Creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:13.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}At Shuijing Mountain, he met Liu Bei, and the two headed back for Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:19.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Along the way, they found a man seeking to serve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:34.97,chs,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}{\i1}...there is a wise man on the mountain, hoping to find a lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:47.47,chs,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}{\i1} The lord seeks wise advisors,\N but still he has no clue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"The lord seeks wise advisers..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"... But still he has no clue."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong, could that man be either \NSleeping Dragon or Fledging Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask where you came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,From all around the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from Yǐngshàng. \NOf the family {\i1}Shàn{\i0}, by the name of {\i1}Fú{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you are recruiting men of talent for your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you listened to my melody, \Nyou have earned my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you, sir, for not refusing me.\NYou have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, let us discuss this at a hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:28.67,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5500,5700)\pos(331.461,670)\bord16}Shàn Fú \N(AKA. Xú Shù \NStyled, Yuánzhí)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That horse must be 'Dilu'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this horse can run a 1,000 li,\N it will bring misfortune to its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, do not ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse galloped across the Tán-Creek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it bring misfotune?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse will curse its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a way to avoid this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, if you have someone in mind you detest, \Nyou should give this horse to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the curse take effect, and then reclaim it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No more problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to hear your melody, \Nand thought it was out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at you, you seemed to be a man of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped you would help me achieve my ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet instead of showing me the way, \Nyou talk of causing petty harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you may need to find another lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long heard of your benevolent reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm shown it was not empty talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Shan Fu, am willing to follow you to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I call myself benevolent! \NI only wish to seek your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, don't be too humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Xinye have sung this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14\i1}"Xinye's Lord, Uncle Liu, \Nblessed is the land, where he would stand."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your benevolence, \Nthe people placed great faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to appoint you as our {\i1}Army-Strategist{\i0}, \Nfor you to train them to achieve great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the 5th year of the Jian'an era.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised a righteous army to destroy each menace of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated Yuan Shao and retook four provinces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have pacified the Wuhuan-tribes and appeased Liaodong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, with the north pacified, I will again march my army!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.40,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Jīng-Xiāng (荆襄) aka. Jing-Province and Xiangyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will first take the lands of {\i1}Jīng-Xiāng{\i0}, \Nthen conquer Eastern Wú!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei had tried earlier to take the capital of Xǔ (Xǔchāng).
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We must kill him while his wings have \Nnot developed to eliminate a future problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals, heed my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Rén.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Diǎn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lü Kuàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lü Xiáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of you will advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:56.75,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5900,200)\pos(260.015,706.427)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead 30,000 troops to garrison at \N{\i1}Fánchéng{\i0}, and scout Liu Biao's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We should speed up preparations to garrison Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei has garrisoned at Xinye, \Nbuilding up his armies and supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This suggests he will take Xǔdū.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He is getting too bold. \NWe must eliminate him early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:32.81,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5800,6500)\pos(243.169,526.356)}Lü Kuàng
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:32.81,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5800,6500)\pos(687.588,481.447)}Lü Xiáng
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we brothers joined the Chancellor, we haven't had great achievements —
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,, — yet still receive the Chancellor's patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're going to Fancheng, we ask of 5,000 elite soldiers —
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,, —  to seize Liu Bei's head and \Ngift it to the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I will let you two \Nlead the elite troops towards Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:51.57,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,490,8150,2620)\pos(1227.792,718.141)}Cáo Rén\NStyled: Zǐxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei will be first to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother! Strategist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that Lü Kuang \Nand Lü Xiang be a match against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:13.69,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5000,5420)\pos(217.133,744.083)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong and I cut them down in two rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! You may sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your plan was ingenious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao wants Lü Kuang and \NLü Xiang to intrude upon our Xinye —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,, — but with only a single plan from our Strategist, \Nhe has now lost two of his warrior-generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, how can Cao Cao be willing to concede at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Xinye has just a few soldiers. \NHow can we counter the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, my lord-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! A large army led by Cao Ren and \NLi Dian is coming towards Xinye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we defeated Lü Kuang and Lü Xiang —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,— a furious Cao Ren led his entire army over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancheng must be empty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We must use this chance to take it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guan Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you will lead thousand soldiers to meet the enemy at Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Two generals just need to follow my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, with their departure, \Nhow can we defend ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We will guard Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong, you will accompany us and await our command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.79,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(1193.071,692.265)}Cáo Rén\NStyled: Zǐxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Dian is defeated! Signal the men to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Change formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, why are you halting our attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the {\i1}Golden Locks of Eight Gates Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong rushed into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Zilong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When I rushed into their formation, a cloud of smoke rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find that Li Dian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cao army changed formation, encasing me in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With much effort, I broke out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and my other troops didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,By the look of it, that formation is hard to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Golden Locks of Eight Gates Formation has eight regiments and gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They are tightly linked together without even a gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If our troops rushed into them, \Nyou will fight a different soldier each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The formation has the soldiers intersect with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The formation never stops turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They can hit you, but you cannot hit them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If a soldier joins them, it will grow the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how brave your soldiers are, \Nthey'll eventually lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the strength of this formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, is there no plan that can defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they are grouped neatly —
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,, — they lack a Supreme Ultimate, \Ntheir center has no commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,General, enter through the Southeast corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you attack the Western Gate, they will rout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your men maintain their flanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have broken through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you are extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You should order our troops not to\N pursue them, but to remain at camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he break through our formation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We will raid Liu Bei's camp tonight \Nwhile he's complacent from victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We will succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be sage men helping Liu Bei now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that our army is at this point, \Nwe must defend Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fall back if we don't succeed tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Liu Bei must have prepared for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Armies aren't run by paranoia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been outmaneuvered!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a ferry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.97,0:24:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a ferry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.12,0:24:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren, halt! I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.66,0:24:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.58,0:25:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gates! Cao Ren's army has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.79,0:25:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gates! Cao Ren's army has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.91,0:25:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren's army has returned! Open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.83,0:25:19.45,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5500,5820)\pos(1228.993,727.447)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Ren, you boor! We already captured Fancheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.40,0:25:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.07,0:25:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come! Let us drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.47,0:25:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategist, thank you! Thank you, elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.04,0:26:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.04,0:26:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.65,0:26:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since this gentleman has joined us, \Nwe've been victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.22,0:26:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew if I were to achieve my undertaking —
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.31,0:26:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,, — I would have to have sage, talented men like him by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.33,0:26:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct, correct, correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.77,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.52,0:26:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.37,0:26:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.75,0:26:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you graced me with your patronage. \NI am merely repaying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.64,0:26:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not receive such respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.82,0:26:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With this gentleman's assistance, we will persevere! Soon our great cause can be realized!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Another round!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.05,0:26:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.72,0:26:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We wish Your Lordship great fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.30,0:27:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.33,0:27:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, we lost Fancheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.40,0:27:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You may punish us!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.78,0:27:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pride led you to ignore warnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.49,0:27:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus you were defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.69,0:27:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because of your past achievements, I shall spare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.47,0:27:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank you for your mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet not too long ago, Liu Bei was handily defeated at Rǔnán under my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you get routed whenever you attack Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.49,0:27:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Golden Locks \Nof Eight Gates Formation has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.13,0:27:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei must have received a great talent to his ranks, planning his next maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.78,0:27:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.75,0:27:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that Liu Bei has gained a judicious advisor called Shan Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:28:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the one who broke our formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.97,0:28:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan Fu? What is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:18.71,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\fade(255,0,255,0,500,6500,6900)\pos(249.346,760)} Chéng Yù \NStyled, Zhòngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Shan Fu is a fake name.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.14,0:28:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He is actually a man from Yingshang, \Nof the family {\i1}Xú{\i0}, by the name of {\i1}Shù{\i0}, styled {\i1}Yuánzhí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was young, he practiced swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.18,0:28:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a forthright personality, and likes to fight against injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Near the end of the {\i1}Zhōngpíng{\i0}-calendar, he killed a corrupt official to avenge a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.85,0:28:34.21,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Zhōngpíng(中平) = 184-189 CE, last calendar era of Emperor Líng of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.69,0:28:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he had no choice but to go into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.10,0:28:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was arrested, \Nhe was asked for his name, but did not reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.37,0:28:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The officials tied him to a cart \Nand drummed in the streets to learn about his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.07,0:28:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because of his heroic deeds, no one identified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.35,0:28:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The office could only put him in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.25,0:29:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Later however, there was 'someone' who freed him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.89,0:29:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu then changed his name, \Nand has since he devoted himself to learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.71,0:29:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He visited famous teachers and \Nbecame enriched with knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.08,0:29:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He often meets with people like Sima Hui about the current state of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.37,0:29:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How does Xu Shu's talent compare to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.60,0:29:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten times as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity! What a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Another talented man falls under Liu Bei's palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.06,0:29:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that his wings are fully developed, how can I not be concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.45,0:29:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Xu Shu serves under Liu Bei —
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.14,0:29:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,, — if you want him under your command, it can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.48,0:30:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you suggesting, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu is a filial man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.21,0:30:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When he lost his father, only his mother stayed in the household.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When his brother Xu Kang passed away, their mother had no one to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.36,0:30:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, you should invite her over to Xudu  —
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.39,0:30:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,, — and have her summon her son with a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.73,0:30:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu will certainly come!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.97,0:30:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.17,0:30:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Send someone to Yingchuan right away, \Nand bring Xu Shu's mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.81,0:30:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you make me come to Xudu?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.17,0:30:39.81,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(509.633,517.72)}Mother of Xu Shu
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.15,0:30:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.97,0:30:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that your son, Xu Yuanzhi, is a prodigy of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.76,0:30:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he is assisting that rebel Liu Bei \Nin undermining the Imperial Court from Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.07,0:30:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not pitiful that such a\Nbeautiful jade fell into the mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.67,0:31:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to come here in order for you to return him back to Xudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.34,0:31:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can petition the Emperor to grant you a hefty reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.36,0:31:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of man is Liu Bei?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.81,0:31:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A lesser man from Zhuo Commandery who claims to be the Emperor's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Treacherous to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As they say; A crook in gentleman's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.48,0:31:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that Liu Xuande is a descendant of the Prince Jìng of Zhōngshān —
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.62,0:31:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,— and of Emperor Jǐng of Hàn's lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.82,0:31:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He treats the virtuous with the utmost respect and has built up a righteous reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.30,0:32:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a hero of this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.03,0:32:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My son is blessed to have such sagacious lord to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.70,0:32:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the Chancellor of the Hàn in name only, because you are its traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.47,0:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie about Liu Xuande being a rebel to have my son turn away from the light into darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.85,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.71,0:32:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.77,0:32:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.01,0:32:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Behead her!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.63,0:32:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.03,0:32:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.17,0:32:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu's mother has angered you to have herself executed —
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.63,0:32:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,— for if you kill her, it will only worsen your reputation and instead make her a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.92,0:32:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By killing her, Xu Shu will either commit suicide or he will devote himself to Liu Bei to avenge her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.62,0:33:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to let her live, so that Xu Shu would be split between two.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.99,0:33:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he stays with Liu Bei, he won't be as dedicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.53,0:33:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Xu Shu's mother remain here, for I have yet another plan to make Xu Shu come.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.69,0:33:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,True. I shall send Xu Shu's mother somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.71,0:33:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.21,0:33:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, how have you been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.11,0:33:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng, you brought me something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.13,0:33:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yuanzhi and I studied together, we were like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.75,0:33:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ma'am, you are like a mother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.87,0:33:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now that Yuanzhi is not here for you, \NI will be for you in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.42,0:34:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng, you are a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.76,0:34:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, you have submitted to Cao Cao. How-
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.69,0:34:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you needn't say more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.87,0:34:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fates are unkind, it is how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.50,0:34:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get the chance, I will send you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.07,0:34:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.37,0:34:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.61,0:34:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do, so I'm afraid I cannot stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.05,0:34:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.07,0:34:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.62,0:34:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.51,0:34:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.23,0:34:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.97,0:34:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Cheng left you another letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.70,0:34:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheng Yu really is a scholarly gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.84,0:34:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have his letter, so I should reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.59,0:34:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fetch me the pen and inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.95,0:34:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.91,0:35:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My lord, someone from Xudu is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.08,0:35:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He was asking where Shan Fu was, he had something to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.11,0:36:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am a servant of Ma'am Xu!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.09,0:36:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have here a letter by her own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.35,0:36:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.52,0:36:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is it that has you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.99,0:36:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.81,0:37:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, say what it is. Don't be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.25,0:37:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.27,0:37:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My real name is {\i1}Xú Shù, {\i0}styled{\i1} Yuánzhí,{\i0} from Yingchuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.23,0:37:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went into hiding,\N I changed my name to Shan Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.37,0:37:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Liu Jingsheng was \Nseeking advisers, so I visited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.31,0:37:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In discussing matters, I came to learn that he was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.31,0:37:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I left a letter of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.78,0:37:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Overnight, I stayed with Master Sima Water-Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.73,0:37:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master criticized me for not recognizing \Na sagacious lord, so he recommended you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.52,0:38:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lucky to have your favor and use of my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.13,0:38:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But for this, now Cao Cao targets me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.49,0:38:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, my mother is now imprisoned in Xudu, under Cao Cao's torment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.45,0:38:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's letter tells thus. I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.22,0:38:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that I do not wish to serve you —
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.56,0:38:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,— but my mother suffers in chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.93,0:38:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I must leave for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.01,0:38:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love between mother and child is the most innate of all. Yuanzhi, you shouldn't consider me before her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.12,0:39:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After you meet with your mother, \Nit will not be too late to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.36,0:39:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi, no need to leave just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.30,0:39:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I implore you to stay with me just this night!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.37,0:39:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I will bid you farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.27,0:39:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I-!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.68,0:39:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.75,0:39:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu takes his leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.61,0:39:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.60,0:39:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.69,0:39:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi is a rare genius in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he saw the ins and outs of our army in Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.28,0:39:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If he goes to Cao Cao, his knowledge will be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.57,0:40:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That would bear ill toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.65,0:40:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you should persist. Do not let him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao will see Yuanzhi did not join him, so he'll kill his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.42,0:40:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yuanzhi hears of this, \Nhe will certainly desire vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.89,0:40:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}To kill a mother \Nto keep the son, is atrocity!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.69,0:40:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Forcing him to stay —
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.55,0:40:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — to sever the bond of \Nmother and son, is depravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.55,0:40:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I would rather die than become vile!
